# Jail objects

The playbook *Makefile.yml* creates descriprions of jail objects.

## Template

See the default template *jail.yml.j2*

## Variables

Edit *Makefile.yml* and fit the variables to your needs.

## Validate the content

Run the playbook and review the variables

```
shell> ansible-playbook Makefile.yml -e debug1=true
```

Run the playbook and review the variables

```
shell> ansible-playbook Makefile.yml -e debug2=true
```

## Create the configuration files

```
shell> ansible-playbook Makefile.yml -e create_obj=true
```
